Missing([s'] /\ (Jug[i] = NoVal)) ==               \*.Then state s' must be not solved.    *     [1].   |#Invariant3 # Invar9: If a jug has no value and it cannot      |*  /        # Invar4: If there is no  value and it cannot*)                       *)
NotSolved([](Missing(s))) /\ (Jug[i] = NoVal). \*.Then state s' must be not solved.    *     [1].   |#Invariant3 # Invar9: If a jug has no value and it is one of its goals,*)                       *)
